%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': {'fontFamily': 'ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant H as MCP Host<br/>(Claude Desktop / CLI / Cowork)
    participant L as Claude (LLM)
    participant S as kkskills-mcp<br/>(stdio | HTTP)
    participant F as skills/*/SKILL.md

    U->>H: ask a question
    H->>L: prompt + tool defs
    Note over L: needs context for<br/>this conversation
    L->>S: call_tool list_skills
    S->>F: read frontmatter from each file
    F-->>S: name + description
    S-->>L: [{name, description}, ...]
    Note over L: pick the relevant skill<br/>(e.g. feedback-additive-changes)
    L->>S: call_tool read_skill(name)
    S->>F: read full SKILL.md
    F-->>S: complete markdown
    S-->>L: SKILL.md content
    Note over L: apply rules + checklist
    L-->>H: response that follows the skill
    H-->>U: final answer
